  <id>io.github.wesenseged.Amharic-bible</id>
  <name>Amharic Bible</name>
  <summary>Read the Holy Bible in Amharic, beautifully designed with Kirigami</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Amharic Bible is a modern, offline Bible reader built with KDE Kirigami and Qt6.
      It features a clean and elegant reading experience, full offline access to the Amharic Bible text,
      and an interface inspired by WordProject.
    </p>
    <p>
      The app supports both light and dark themes, adjustable font size,
      and quick navigation between books and chapters.
    </p>
  </description>
